title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You might need more rest and relaxation before you can fully commit to your agenda. You think you must push through any mental fog, but it may be more useful to take some time to unplug than to slog through the drudgery of errands and tasks today. The inspiration you gain from honoring dreamy Neptunes dynamic square to the adventurous Sagittarius Moon in your 3rd House of Distractions makes fulfilling your responsibilities a merrier proposition. Thankfully, you won't need a lot of downtime before your battery is recharged. Your mind and body will thank you for making them a priority. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
